#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _posts/2023-08-02-quarkus-3-2-3-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Quarkus 3.2.3.Final released - Maintenance release"
msgstr "Quarkus 3.2.3.Final 发布 - 维护版本"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: synopsis
#: _posts/2023-08-02-quarkus-3-2-3-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Quarkus 3.2.3.Final is the third maintenance release of our 3.2 release train."
msgstr "Quarkus 3.2.3.Final 是我们 3.2 版本系列的第三个维护版本。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-08-02-quarkus-3-2-3-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"August is upon us but we are still steadily publishing new Quarkus releases.\n"
"Today, we released Quarkus 3.2.3.Final, the third maintenance release of our 3.2 release train."
msgstr "八月已经来临，但我们仍在稳步发布新的 Quarkus 版本。今天，我们发布了 Quarkus 3.2.3.Final，这是我们 3.2 版本系列的第三个维护版本。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-08-02-quarkus-3-2-3-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "It should be a safe upgrade for anyone already using 3.2."
msgstr "对于已经在使用 3.2 版的用户来说，这应该是一次安全的升级。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-08-02-quarkus-3-2-3-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Note that this version upgrades Hibernate Search to 6.2\n"
"as we wanted to offer full support for Elasticsearch 8 in Quarkus 3.2.\n"
"If you are using Hibernate Search, have another look at the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.2#hibernate-search[dedicated section of the 3.2 migration guide]."
msgstr "请注意，该版本将 Hibernate Search 升级到了 6.2，因为我们希望在 Quarkus 3.2 中提供对 Elasticsearch 8 的全面支持。如果你正在使用 Hibernate Search，请再次查看 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.2#hibernate-search[3.2 迁移指南中的专门部分] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-08-02-quarkus-3-2-3-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you are not already using 3.2, please refer to the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.2[Quarkus 3.2 migration guide]."
msgstr "如果您尚未使用 3.2，请参阅 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.2[Quarkus 3.2 迁移指南] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2023-08-02-quarkus-3-2-3-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "And if you are not already using 3.0, please refer to https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-final-released/[the Quarkus 3.0 announcement] and in particular the section about the https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-final-released/#upgrading[upgrade path to 3.0] together with the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.1[3.1 migration guide] and https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.2[Quarkus 3.2 migration guide]."
msgstr "如果您尚未使用 3.0，请参阅 link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-final-released/[Quarkus 3.0 公告] ，特别是有关 3. link:https://quarkus.io/blog/quarkus-3-0-final-released/#upgrading[0 升级路径] 的部分，以及 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.1[3.1 迁移指南] 和 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.2[Quarkus 3.2 迁移指南] 。"

