msgstr "你可以在 GitHub 上获取 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.2.3.Final[3.2.3.Final 的完整更新日志] 和 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/releases/tag/3.2.3.Final[3.2.3.Final 的完整更新日志] 。"

